headline: BlackRock's Fink made Trump happy with Panama Canal deal. The cost may be an unhappy China.
summary: BlackRock CEO Larry Fink orchestrated the Panama Canal port takeover that made President Donald Trump happy, but the cost may be an angry Xi Jinping.
